{"tid":340230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵都叫一地兩檢，咁羅湖都叫一地兩檢啦","createTime":"2017-07-29T17:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T11:36:25.000Z","uid":62226,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4e33c3f11e9bf926bf0d5b8b3a79c34027d3dc","tid":340230,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"去到中國海關層同之後既月台同列車都係中國範圍<br />\n咁同羅湖行過深圳河之後就係中國範圍有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f852d9ea34e8e68a07c8f46f063d34364133c4","tid":340230,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T17:55:15.000Z","msg":"而家呢個方案根本係兩地兩檢<br />\n兩地分別係中國香港特區西九龍同中國(深圳)西九龍<br />\n要搞清楚唔係真一地兩檢"},{"pid":"ba7d63a1e779580e6ea8d109e1995efb783df5bc","tid":340230,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:11:27.000Z","msg":"根本就係兩地兩檢.<br />\n租地借地,係違反基本法<br />\n割咗地, 即係兩地."},{"pid":"2235c049630e7bbc6041e51a832651d3bc1b7f4a","tid":340230,"uid":24547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:17:10.000Z","msg":"係割地兩檢"},{"pid":"2acba26801bab8f2ce5f214c55e41d734fefd9eb","tid":340230,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"好多五毛比負皮"},{"pid":"d78b194310cdf366e603cebdef783706fd826560","tid":340230,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多五毛比負皮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bc21990e023f9ab6ac27e4fbc602130604bfa7","tid":340230,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"租借就係違反基本法<br />\n割地。割咗就係叫&quot;大陸&quot;<br />\n香港檢完，大陸又要檢<br />\n根本係2地2檢"},{"pid":"5ffbc2b782bcc14e38f74bd8447469df39a87ea5","tid":340230,"uid":123050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"高鐵配合埋一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這張圖說明了奧斯威辛集中營的恐怖勢力<br />\n從西元1941年起，蓋世太保向集中營運送了捷克人、斯洛伐克人、俄國人、法國人等24個國家的囚犯<br />\n以及所有被佔領國的大批猶太人和吉卜賽人<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://pic.pimg.tw/julia116/1432913170-556411930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjulia116%2F1432913170-556411930.jpg&h=44d9d831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過程中，可以不斷聽到導覽員用『My people』來稱呼在集中營受難的波蘭人<br />\n幾度我都感覺到她聲音裡的哽咽，呼吸也變的急促<br />\n在這樣的氣氛下，情緒很難不被影響，我又忍不住紅了眼眶<br />\n其實不難理解，對波蘭來說，先是被德國侵占了五年，又在共產主義的統治下四十年<br />\n納粹以次等公民對待波蘭人，將死亡集中營建在他們土地上，奧斯威辛集中營成了這塊土地上永遠的痛<br />\n原本淳樸單純的小鎮，只能永遠背負著無法承受的歷史包袱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港已經變左中共實驗城市? 高鐵就係「死亡末日列車」?</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/343998/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/343998/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7c22d9ca4afb9568f1bb7e94c92fa31ef10f149c","tid":340230,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"香港=中國，檢條毛"}]}